1
00:01:43,521 --> 00:01:45,621
- OUR SWORN ENEMY, NARAKU,

2
00:01:45,654 --> 00:01:48,754
BECOMES INCREASINGLY POWERFUL
AS HE TAKES POSSESSION

3
00:01:48,787 --> 00:01:51,454
OF MORE AND MORE
SACRED JEWEL SHARDS.

4
00:01:51,487 --> 00:01:52,654
EACH AND EVERY TIME,

5
00:01:52,687 --> 00:01:55,187
HE MANIPULATES
PEOPLE AND SITUATIONS

6
00:01:55,221 --> 00:01:56,787
IN ORDER TO GAIN MORE POWER

7
00:01:56,821 --> 00:01:59,787
WITHOUT GETTING HIMSELF
DIRECTLY INVOLVED.

8
00:01:59,821 --> 00:02:03,421
WE HAVE TO FIND NARAKU
AND DESTROY HIM QUICKLY

9
00:02:03,454 --> 00:02:05,654
TO UNDO THE CURSE HE PLACED
ON MIROKU'S HAND

10
00:02:05,687 --> 00:02:09,854
AND TO HELP SANGO
RESCUE HER BROTHER KOHAKU.

11
00:02:17,254 --> 00:02:19,954
[CRICKETS CHIRPING]

12
00:02:24,587 --> 00:02:27,154
- [SNORING]

13
00:02:35,387 --> 00:02:37,954
- [SNIFFING]

14
00:02:38,954 --> 00:02:40,554
HMM?

15
00:02:40,921 --> 00:02:42,354
UNH!

16
00:02:43,054 --> 00:02:46,287
- MMM...HMM?

17
00:02:53,221 --> 00:02:55,487
- [SNIFFING]

18
00:02:55,521 --> 00:02:56,154
GRR!

19
00:02:56,187 --> 00:02:58,821
- WHAT'S THE MATTER? INUYASHA?

20
00:02:58,854 --> 00:03:00,554
- I SMELL TROUBLE COMING.

21
00:03:00,587 --> 00:03:02,754
- [GASPS]

22
00:03:02,787 --> 00:03:03,921
- NARAKU.

23
00:03:03,954 --> 00:03:05,887
- OH!

24
00:03:08,887 --> 00:03:11,487
[WIND BLOWING]

25
00:03:17,354 --> 00:03:20,954
- HMM. THE SCENT OF THE WIND
HAS CHANGED.

26
00:03:20,987 --> 00:03:23,554
- LORD SESSHOMARU!

27
00:03:23,587 --> 00:03:25,254
[PANTING]

28
00:03:25,287 --> 00:03:26,721
YOUNG RIN HAS BEEN ABDUCTED!

29
00:03:26,754 --> 00:03:28,121
NARAKU'S INCARNATION, KAGURA,

30
00:03:28,154 --> 00:03:32,387
APPEARED OUT OF NOWHERE
AND TOOK OFF WITH RIN!

31
00:03:35,487 --> 00:03:39,354
- LET ME REASSURE YOU,
LORD SESSHOMARU.

32
00:03:40,687 --> 00:03:43,221
[BUZZING]

33
00:03:44,287 --> 00:03:45,987
- IF YOU HEED MY REQUEST,

34
00:03:46,021 --> 00:03:49,221
I SHALL RETURN RIN
IN GOOD HEALTH.

35
00:03:50,654 --> 00:03:52,821
- AH! IT'S NARAKU!

36
00:03:52,854 --> 00:03:53,787
- WE MEET AGAIN.

37
00:03:53,821 --> 00:03:57,787
SO, WHAT DO YOU HAVE
UP YOUR SLEEVE THIS TIME?

38
00:03:57,821 --> 00:03:59,021
- NOTHING SPECIAL.

39
00:03:59,054 --> 00:04:03,221
I SIMPLY WANT YOU
TO KILL INUYASHA.

40
00:04:09,621 --> 00:04:12,921
- HUH. WHY ARE YOU
GOING TO ALL THIS TROUBLE

41
00:04:12,954 --> 00:04:16,254
FOR SOMETHING SO TRIVIAL?

42
00:04:21,687 --> 00:04:26,287
- AAH! WHAT IS THAT?!

43
00:04:26,321 --> 00:04:29,521
A DEMON PUPPET?

44
00:04:29,554 --> 00:04:31,287
- DOES NARAKU HONESTLY BELIEVE

45
00:04:31,321 --> 00:04:33,087
THAT HE CAN THREATEN ME
INTO ACTION

46
00:04:33,121 --> 00:04:36,521
BY ENDANGERING THE LIFE
OF A MERE MORTAL?

47
00:04:36,554 --> 00:04:39,687
- WILL YOU TURN YOUR BACK
ON THE GIRL?

48
00:04:39,721 --> 00:04:42,054
WILL YOU FORSAKE HER?

49
00:04:42,687 --> 00:04:43,454
WAIT!!

50
00:04:43,487 --> 00:04:45,487
LORD SESSHOMARU,
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

51
00:04:45,521 --> 00:04:47,121
[BUZZING]

52
00:04:47,154 --> 00:04:49,554
- WHERE ARE YOU HEADED, MY LORD?

53
00:04:52,287 --> 00:04:54,954
[THUNDER RUMBLES]

54
00:05:09,887 --> 00:05:14,587
- SO, SESSHOMARU, YOU'VE COME.

55
00:05:14,621 --> 00:05:16,221
HMM.

56
00:05:17,821 --> 00:05:20,387
- [PANTING]

57
00:05:21,321 --> 00:05:22,754
UNH! UNH!

58
00:05:22,787 --> 00:05:24,687
- ARE YOU SURE
IT'S NARAKU YOU SMELL?

59
00:05:24,721 --> 00:05:26,854
- YEAH. I KNOW THAT STENCH!

60
00:05:26,887 --> 00:05:28,021
LOOK OUT, NARAKU!

61
00:05:28,054 --> 00:05:30,387
I'LL FIND YOU FOR SURE
THIS TIME!

62
00:05:30,421 --> 00:05:31,521
AND I'LL KILL YOU!

63
00:05:31,554 --> 00:05:34,721
- HE'S GONE OUT OF HIS WAY
TO HIDE HIMSELF ALL THIS TIME.

64
00:05:34,754 --> 00:05:36,721
WHY WOULD HE SHOW UP NOW?

65
00:05:36,754 --> 00:05:39,721
- YES, THAT BOTHERS ME, TOO.

66
00:05:53,021 --> 00:05:55,354
- [GROANING]

67
00:05:55,387 --> 00:05:56,687
OH, NOW I REMEMBER.

68
00:05:56,721 --> 00:06:00,254
THAT KAGURA LADY TOOK ME AWAY.

69
00:06:00,721 --> 00:06:02,554
- IT'S YOU AGAIN!

70
00:06:03,021 --> 00:06:05,554
AAH! UNH!

71
00:06:05,587 --> 00:06:07,421
- I WAS ABDUCTED.

72
00:06:09,587 --> 00:06:11,287
WHERE AM I?

73
00:06:11,321 --> 00:06:12,754
HUH?

74
00:06:17,654 --> 00:06:19,221
WHO ARE YOU?

75
00:06:26,321 --> 00:06:28,121
- NO, YOU CAN'T GO OUTSIDE!

76
00:06:28,154 --> 00:06:29,854
- I HAVE TO GET BACK.

77
00:06:29,887 --> 00:06:32,387
[GASPS]

78
00:06:37,654 --> 00:06:40,187
- [ROARS]

79
00:06:53,187 --> 00:06:54,954
- I TOLD YOU NOT TO GO OUTSIDE.

80
00:06:54,987 --> 00:06:58,387
IF YOU DO,
THEY'LL TEAR YOU APART.

81
00:06:58,821 --> 00:06:59,654
- WHO ARE YOU?

82
00:06:59,687 --> 00:07:01,587
WERE YOU BROUGHT HERE
AGAINST YOUR WILL,

83
00:07:01,621 --> 00:07:02,754
LIKE I WAS?

84
00:07:02,787 --> 00:07:04,254
WE COULD RUN AWAY TOGETHER!

85
00:07:04,287 --> 00:07:06,054
- MY JOB IS TO GUARD YOU.

86
00:07:06,087 --> 00:07:08,054
- [SIGHS]

87
00:07:08,087 --> 00:07:10,554
OH, I SEE.

88
00:07:14,054 --> 00:07:17,354
- OH! YOU DIDN'T
TELL ME YOUR NAME.

89
00:07:17,387 --> 00:07:19,587
YOU CAN CALL ME RIN,
IF YOU WANT.

90
00:07:19,621 --> 00:07:20,321
HOW OLD ARE YOU?

91
00:07:20,354 --> 00:07:21,987
AND HOW COME
YOU'RE A GUARD HERE?

92
00:07:22,021 --> 00:07:24,121
DOES THAT MEAN YOU'RE A DEMON
LIKE THE OTHERS?

93
00:07:24,154 --> 00:07:26,287
TELL ME,
WHAT DO YOU LIKE TO EAT?

94
00:07:26,321 --> 00:07:28,454
DO YOU LIKE MELONS?

95
00:07:29,154 --> 00:07:30,354
- YEAH, I GUESS.

96
00:07:30,387 --> 00:07:31,787
YOU SURE TALK A LOT.

97
00:07:31,821 --> 00:07:33,287
- HMM?

98
00:07:34,454 --> 00:07:35,721
[SIGHS]

99
00:07:35,754 --> 00:07:40,587
I KNOW, BUT I GET SCARED
WHEN I'M NOT TALKING.

100
00:07:40,621 --> 00:07:45,121
I WONDER IF LORD SESSHOMARU
WILL COME TO RESCUE ME?

101
00:07:48,721 --> 00:07:51,321
[WIND BLOWING]

102
00:07:53,521 --> 00:07:55,187
- IF I MAY SO BOLD AS TO ASK,

103
00:07:55,221 --> 00:07:58,287
HOW DO YOU PLAN
TO APPROACH THIS, MY LORD?

104
00:07:59,154 --> 00:08:04,187
WHY DID YOU STOP?
IS SOMETHING THE MATTER?

105
00:08:04,854 --> 00:08:07,087
- NARAKU'S CASTLE IS HERE.

106
00:08:07,121 --> 00:08:08,454
- HUH?

107
00:08:08,487 --> 00:08:10,554
UHH...

108
00:08:10,954 --> 00:08:14,054
I DON'T SEE A CASTLE, MY LORD.

109
00:08:20,154 --> 00:08:22,787
[JAKEN SCREAMS]

110
00:08:25,121 --> 00:08:27,754
[JAKEN WHIMPERS]

111
00:08:27,954 --> 00:08:30,687
THE BARRIER HAS OPENED UP.

112
00:08:39,487 --> 00:08:41,387
MY LORD!

113
00:08:49,887 --> 00:08:52,754
[JAKEN WHIMPERING]

114
00:08:52,787 --> 00:08:54,254
WAIT!

115
00:08:54,287 --> 00:08:58,621
- YOU PURPOSELY LEAVE YOUR SCENT
TO REVEAL YOUR CASTLE

116
00:08:58,654 --> 00:09:02,721
SO THAT I WILL FOLLOW YOU HERE.

117
00:09:03,021 --> 00:09:06,487
- WOULD YOU HAVE COME OTHERWISE?

118
00:09:12,187 --> 00:09:13,187
- OH!

119
00:09:13,221 --> 00:09:15,521
- I MUST INFORM YOU
THAT THE MORTAL GIRL YOU SEEK

120
00:09:15,554 --> 00:09:17,254
IS NOT HERE IN MY CASTLE.

121
00:09:17,287 --> 00:09:18,987
SHE WOULD NEVER
BE ABLE TO SURVIVE

122
00:09:19,021 --> 00:09:22,454
THE AIRLESS ATMOSPHERE
OF THIS POISONOUS MIASMA.

123
00:09:22,487 --> 00:09:26,054
THE GIRL IS UNDER MY PROTECTION
OUTSIDE THE CASTLE WALLS.

124
00:09:26,087 --> 00:09:28,887
I ASSURE YOU SHE IS UNHARMED...

125
00:09:28,921 --> 00:09:29,921
FOR NOW.

126
00:09:29,954 --> 00:09:33,087
- NARAKU, DO ME THE HONOR
OF AT LEAST RECOGNIZING

127
00:09:33,121 --> 00:09:36,554
THAT I AM NOT HERE
SIMPLY TO SAVE RIN.

128
00:09:36,587 --> 00:09:38,154
- HUH?

129
00:09:38,187 --> 00:09:39,054
- OF COURSE.

130
00:09:39,087 --> 00:09:41,721
YOU OF ALL PEOPLE
SEEM TO DESPISE

131
00:09:41,754 --> 00:09:42,954
TAKING ORDERS FROM OTHERS.

132
00:09:42,987 --> 00:09:46,687
YOU WILL NOT KILL INUYASHA
WHEN TOLD TO DO SO.

133
00:09:46,721 --> 00:09:49,254
NOR DID YOU COME
TO LOOK FOR THE GIRL.

134
00:09:49,287 --> 00:09:54,221
I REALIZE THAT YOU
ARE HERE TO KILL ME.

135
00:09:54,254 --> 00:09:55,387
- HMM.

136
00:09:55,421 --> 00:09:58,421
YOU SOUND AS IF YOU BELIEVE
YOU'VE LED ME INTO YOUR TRAP.

137
00:09:58,454 --> 00:10:01,754
PERHAPS LATER
I'LL HAVE YOU EXPLAIN YOURSELF.

138
00:10:01,787 --> 00:10:08,221
IF YOU SHOULD SURVIVE THE NIGHT,
THAT IS.

139
00:10:08,254 --> 00:10:09,387
- [CHUCKLES]

140
00:10:09,421 --> 00:10:15,187
SESSHOMARU, YOU WILL ASSIST ME
WHETHER YOU LIKE IT OR NOT.

141
00:10:15,221 --> 00:10:17,787
- [PANTING]

142
00:10:18,654 --> 00:10:19,954
UNH!

143
00:10:19,987 --> 00:10:20,954
UNH!

144
00:10:20,987 --> 00:10:21,987
UNH!

145
00:10:22,021 --> 00:10:23,921
- INUYASHA, WAIT FOR US!

146
00:10:23,954 --> 00:10:26,287
- SLOW DOWN, WE'RE LOSING YOU!

147
00:10:26,321 --> 00:10:27,221
- UNH!

148
00:10:27,254 --> 00:10:28,187
WHAT'S THE HOLDUP?

149
00:10:28,221 --> 00:10:32,221
- I CAN SENSE
A SACRED JEWEL SHARD.

150
00:10:32,254 --> 00:10:33,021
- HUH?

151
00:10:33,054 --> 00:10:35,621
- UH.
- HUH.

152
00:10:36,021 --> 00:10:38,487
- IT'S COMING FROM OVER THERE.

153
00:10:40,121 --> 00:10:43,354
- SO YOU THINK THE SHARD IS
IN THOSE MOUNTAINS OVER THERE?

154
00:10:43,387 --> 00:10:44,521
- WHAT SHOULD WE DO?

155
00:10:44,554 --> 00:10:45,821
- WE'LL GO AFTER
THE JEWEL SHARD.

156
00:10:45,854 --> 00:10:47,221
[THUNDER RUMBLES]

157
00:10:47,254 --> 00:10:50,821
INUYASHA, YOU GO AND TRY
AND FIND NARAKU'S CASTLE.

158
00:10:50,854 --> 00:10:53,454
- RIGHT. MAKE SURE
YOU GET THE JEWEL.

159
00:10:53,487 --> 00:10:56,154
- BE CAREFUL, INUYASHA.

160
00:10:56,187 --> 00:10:59,087
UHH...OH.

161
00:10:59,121 --> 00:11:01,654
[THUNDER]

162
00:11:09,254 --> 00:11:10,521
- I WONDER WHAT'S GOING ON?

163
00:11:10,554 --> 00:11:12,887
I'M STARTING TO LOSE
NARAKU'S SCENT.

164
00:11:12,921 --> 00:11:13,954
UNH!

165
00:11:13,987 --> 00:11:16,521
DOES IT MEAN THE BARRIER'S
BACK UP AROUND THE CASTLE?

166
00:11:16,554 --> 00:11:18,754
I'VE GOT TO HURRY
BEFORE I LOSE HIM.

167
00:11:18,787 --> 00:11:20,954
A BARRIER!

168
00:11:20,987 --> 00:11:23,354
HUH! IT WON'T STOP ME!

169
00:11:23,387 --> 00:11:25,754
WINDSCAR!

170
00:11:29,587 --> 00:11:32,421
- AH!
- UNH!

171
00:11:36,921 --> 00:11:39,554
- THE WINDSCAR DIDN'T WORK.

172
00:11:46,387 --> 00:11:48,921
- HE WON'T GET AWAY THIS TIME.

173
00:11:49,987 --> 00:11:51,521
UNH!

174
00:11:51,554 --> 00:11:52,987
UNH!

175
00:11:56,887 --> 00:11:58,421
- [NARAKU CHUCKLES]

176
00:11:58,454 --> 00:12:03,221
LORD SESSHOMARU,
I'M HONORED BY YOUR VISIT.

177
00:12:03,254 --> 00:12:09,521
SO IN RETURN, I WILL
GLADLY ACCEPT YOUR CHALLENGE.

178
00:12:14,587 --> 00:12:16,954
- AAH! WHAT'S HE BECOME?!

179
00:12:21,687 --> 00:12:25,554
- HUH. A COLLECTION
OF REJECTED DEMONS.

180
00:12:25,587 --> 00:12:29,154
THIS IS YOUR TRUE FORM, NARAKU?

181
00:12:29,187 --> 00:12:31,587
- TRUE FORM? NO.

182
00:12:31,621 --> 00:12:35,621
MY BODY IS FAR
FROM BEING COMPLETE.

183
00:12:38,287 --> 00:12:40,321
- [JAKEN YELPS]

184
00:12:40,354 --> 00:12:42,921
[WHIMPERING]

185
00:12:45,587 --> 00:12:51,121
- HUH. YOU'LL DESTROY ME
FOR REFUSING TO DO AS YOU WISH?

186
00:12:57,654 --> 00:12:59,021
- I DON'T UNDERSTAND.

187
00:12:59,054 --> 00:13:03,654
HOW WOULD NARAKU BENEFIT
BY SESSHOMARU'S DEATH?

188
00:13:03,687 --> 00:13:07,687
COULD THAT BE
WHAT NARAKU'S PLANNING?

189
00:13:13,121 --> 00:13:16,087
- THE SACRED JEWEL SHARD
IS NEARBY.

190
00:13:16,121 --> 00:13:17,487
- I DON'T LIKE THIS,

191
00:13:17,521 --> 00:13:21,121
CONSIDERING WE'RE SO CLOSE
TO NARAKU'S CASTLE.

192
00:13:21,154 --> 00:13:22,987
- YEAH, I AGREE.

193
00:13:23,021 --> 00:13:27,021
I THINK THAT
THERE'S JUST ONE SHARD.

194
00:13:27,054 --> 00:13:28,021
COME TO THINK OF IT,

195
00:13:28,054 --> 00:13:33,121
SANGO'S BROTHER KOHAKU
HAD ONLY ONE SHARD IN HIM.

196
00:13:40,354 --> 00:13:41,321
- HMM?

197
00:13:41,354 --> 00:13:43,954
- IS IT KOHAKU?

198
00:13:49,654 --> 00:13:51,321
- [CHEWING]

199
00:13:51,354 --> 00:13:53,587
- THIS MELON IS REALLY SWEET.

200
00:13:53,621 --> 00:13:56,454
- AHH. WOULD YOU LIKE
ANOTHER PIECE?

201
00:13:56,487 --> 00:13:58,721
- YES. THANK YOU.

202
00:13:58,754 --> 00:14:00,654
- HERE YOU ARE.

203
00:14:01,121 --> 00:14:06,021
IF YOU LIKE IT THAT MUCH,
I CAN ALWAYS GO STEAL SOME MORE.

204
00:14:08,787 --> 00:14:11,954
YOU DON'T
REMEMBER ANYTHING, KOHAKU?

205
00:14:11,987 --> 00:14:14,121
- NO, I DON'T.

206
00:14:15,021 --> 00:14:18,387
- NOT EVEN YOUR MOTHER
OR YOUR FATHER?

207
00:14:19,321 --> 00:14:21,287
- I'VE FORGOTTEN.

208
00:14:21,321 --> 00:14:22,987
- HUH.

209
00:14:23,021 --> 00:14:26,087
I'VE NEVER HEARD OF A PERSON
FORGETTING EVERYTHING.

210
00:14:26,121 --> 00:14:28,521
- IT'S NOT THAT.

211
00:14:28,554 --> 00:14:29,554
IT'S JUST THAT...

212
00:14:29,587 --> 00:14:31,654
I'M AFRAID I MIGHT REMEMBER
SOMETHING FRIGHTENING.

213
00:14:31,687 --> 00:14:36,921
- I GUESS EVERYONE HAS
THINGS THAT THEY DON'T
WANT TO REMEMBER.

214
00:14:36,954 --> 00:14:37,754
- HUH?

215
00:14:37,787 --> 00:14:38,921
- I'M THE SAME.

216
00:14:38,954 --> 00:14:41,921
MY PARENTS AND BROTHERS
WERE ATTACKED BY THIEVES.

217
00:14:41,954 --> 00:14:45,587
THEY TRIED TO GET AWAY,
BUT THEY WERE KILLED.

218
00:14:45,621 --> 00:14:49,854
I STILL HAVE NIGHTMARES
ABOUT THE NIGHT IT HAPPENED.

219
00:14:49,887 --> 00:14:52,121
IT STILL SCARES ME.

220
00:14:52,154 --> 00:14:53,287
AM I TALKING TOO MUCH?

221
00:14:53,321 --> 00:14:57,354
YOU KNOW, PEOPLE ARE ALWAYS
TELLING ME TO BE QUIET.

222
00:14:57,387 --> 00:14:58,587
- IT'S OK.

223
00:14:58,621 --> 00:15:00,787
I DON'T MIND
IF YOU KEEP TALKING.

224
00:15:00,821 --> 00:15:03,154
I DON'T GET TO TALK MUCH.

225
00:15:03,187 --> 00:15:05,721
[BUZZING]

226
00:15:11,321 --> 00:15:13,821
[ROARS]

227
00:15:16,287 --> 00:15:17,854
- WHAT'S THE MATTER?

228
00:15:17,887 --> 00:15:19,654
- KEEP QUIET.

229
00:15:27,854 --> 00:15:29,454
- UH! IT'S HER AGAIN!

230
00:15:29,487 --> 00:15:34,054
HER FACE IS
THE ONLY THING I REMEMBER.

231
00:15:34,087 --> 00:15:37,454
I CAN'T GET HER OUT OF MY MIND.

232
00:15:37,487 --> 00:15:39,987
[GROANS]

233
00:15:45,687 --> 00:15:47,154
- UNH!

234
00:15:48,387 --> 00:15:50,021
AH!

235
00:15:51,921 --> 00:15:53,087
COME BACK HERE!

236
00:15:53,121 --> 00:15:54,054
- I'D THINK TWICE

237
00:15:54,087 --> 00:15:56,521
ABOUT FORCING THIS BOY
TO REMEMBER EVERYTHING.

238
00:15:56,554 --> 00:15:59,087
HIS PAST REALLY
WOULD DESTROY HIM.

239
00:15:59,121 --> 00:16:00,521
LET THE POOR LAD DIE IN BLISS,

240
00:16:00,554 --> 00:16:04,187
FREE FROM ALL THOSE
TERRIBLE MEMORIES.

241
00:16:08,321 --> 00:16:11,454
- KOHAKU, ARE YOU INSIDE?

242
00:16:11,487 --> 00:16:13,087
KOHAKU.

243
00:16:37,036 --> 00:16:38,503
- HMM.

244
00:16:52,269 --> 00:16:55,469
- NARAKU, YOU'RE SUCH
A LOWLY DEMON.

245
00:16:55,503 --> 00:17:00,169
YOU WILL NEVER HAVE THE POWER
OR RESOURCES TO HARM ME.

246
00:17:00,203 --> 00:17:02,669
- HA HA HA!

247
00:17:08,436 --> 00:17:09,903
- UH!

248
00:17:11,569 --> 00:17:13,169
- HUH?

249
00:17:15,503 --> 00:17:16,936
UNH!

250
00:17:18,369 --> 00:17:19,403
UNH!

251
00:17:19,436 --> 00:17:20,836
UNH!

252
00:17:20,869 --> 00:17:22,303
UNH!

253
00:17:25,269 --> 00:17:30,769
- HUH. HOW LONG DO YOU INTEND
TO KEEP UP THIS LUDICROUS FARCE?

254
00:17:32,069 --> 00:17:33,669
- [NARAKU CHUCKLES]

255
00:17:33,703 --> 00:17:35,336
EVERY TIME YOU HACK AWAY
A PIECE OF ME,

256
00:17:35,369 --> 00:17:38,903
YOU'RE SLOWLY COVERED
BY PIECES OF MY FLESH.

257
00:17:38,936 --> 00:17:40,103
AND THEN...

258
00:17:40,136 --> 00:17:41,569
- I KNEW IT!

259
00:17:41,603 --> 00:17:46,969
NARAKU IS TRYING TO ABSORB
SESSHOMARU INTO HIS OWN BODY.

260
00:17:59,969 --> 00:18:01,803
- HUH.

261
00:18:01,836 --> 00:18:04,369
[PANTING]

262
00:18:06,036 --> 00:18:09,203
HUH? WHAT'S GOING ON?

263
00:18:09,236 --> 00:18:11,503
SESSHOMARU'S SCENT
COMES THIS FAR,

264
00:18:11,536 --> 00:18:13,736
BUT THEN IT VANISHES.

265
00:18:16,336 --> 00:18:17,336
- UH.

266
00:18:17,369 --> 00:18:21,236
- WAIT! MAYBE THIS
IS NARAKU'S CASTLE!

267
00:18:21,703 --> 00:18:23,336
UH! UH!

268
00:18:23,369 --> 00:18:26,403
UNH!

269
00:18:26,436 --> 00:18:28,403
THAT DEMONIC AURA
AND TOXIC GASES,

270
00:18:28,436 --> 00:18:31,136
