272
00:18:32,436 --> 00:18:33,603
UNH!

273
00:18:33,636 --> 00:18:35,436
AAH!

274
00:18:41,369 --> 00:18:43,903
TETSUSAIGA!

275
00:18:49,003 --> 00:18:51,803
