THROUGH MY BARRIER.

279
00:19:04,903 --> 00:19:06,703
KAGURA, AFTER HIM.

280
00:19:06,736 --> 00:19:08,636
- HUH? HMM.

281
00:19:08,669 --> 00:19:10,836
- AN UNEXPECTED GUEST, NARAKU?

282
00:19:10,869 --> 00:19:12,669
HOW VERY UNFORTUNATE FOR HIM.

283
00:19:12,703 --> 00:19:16,769
I ASSURE YOU, HIS JOURNEY HERE
WILL HAVE BEEN IN VAIN.

284
00:19:18,203 --> 00:19:20,636
BY THE TIME HE ARRIVES,

285
00:19:20,669 --> 00:19:22,669
YOU'LL BE DEAD!

286
00:19:31,803 --> 00:19:33,603
- [CHUCKLES]

287
00:19:33,636 --> 00:19:34,603
JUST A LITTLE LONGER.

288
00:19:34,636 --> 00:19:37,936
SOON YOU WILL BE
ABSORBED INTO MY BODY.

289
00:19:37,969 --> 00:19:41,503
YOU WILL BE ONE WITH MY FLESH.

290
00:19:43,036 --> 00:19:45,136
- UH! INUYASHA!

291
00:19:49,936 --> 00:19:53,636
THE TETSUSAIGA'S BLADE IS RED.

292
00:19:54,069 --> 00:19:55,169
- HMM? KAGURA.

293
00:19:55,203 --> 00:19:58,536
- SO IT WAS YOU WHO BROKE
THROUGH THE BARRIER, INUYASHA.

294
00:19:58,569 --> 00:20:00,169
- IN THE FLESH, KAGURA.

295
00:20:00,203 --> 00:20:02,036
TAKE MY ADVICE: STAND BACK.

296
00:20:02,069 --> 00:20:05,003
YOU'RE NO MATCH FOR ME
ANY LONGER.

297
00:20:05,503 --> 00:20:07,536
BACK OFF AND LET ME PASS,

298
00:20:07,569 --> 00:20:10,236
OR I'LL HAVE TO KILL YOU.

299
00:20:12,236 --> 00:20:14,769
[BUZZING]

300
00:20:16,369 --> 00:20:17,436
- THE SAIMYOUSHOU.

301
00:20:17,469 --> 00:20:22,836
I CAN'T LET YOU PASS,
BECAUSE I'M UNDER WATCH MYSELF.

302
00:20:23,469 --> 00:20:24,503
- HUH?

303
00:20:24,536 --> 00:20:27,503
- I'D BETTER AT LEAST
PUT ON A SHOW OF FIGHTING HIM.

304
00:20:28,569 --> 00:20:30,269
- HUH?

305
00:20:30,303 --> 00:20:31,736
UNH!

306
00:20:32,903 --> 00:20:34,536
HUH? WHAT'S GOING ON?

307
00:20:34,569 --> 00:20:37,169
KAGURA'S WIND
HAS NO POWER AT ALL.

308
00:20:37,203 --> 00:20:40,469
IF YOU'RE GOING TO FIGHT ME,
YOU BETTER GET SERIOUS!

309
00:20:40,503 --> 00:20:42,469
- UNH!

310
00:20:42,503 --> 00:20:43,269
- AAH!

311
00:20:43,303 --> 00:20:45,403
YOU'LL HAVE TO DO
BETTER THAN THAT!

312
00:20:48,136 --> 00:20:52,203
- THEY KNOW I'M NOT SERIOUS
ABOUT FIGHTING HIM.

313
00:20:52,236 --> 00:20:55,036
I'LL HAVE TO TAKE THIS
UP A LEVEL.

314
00:20:58,769 --> 00:21:01,303
[SNARLING]

315
00:21:03,736 --> 00:21:05,203
- HMM.

316
00:21:07,069 --> 00:21:11,103
PERFECT. THEY CAN
TAKE CARE OF HIM.

317
00:21:12,169 --> 00:21:14,703
- HA! NO PROBLEM.

318
00:21:14,736 --> 00:21:17,269
TRY THIS. WINDSCAR!

319
00:21:21,436 --> 00:21:23,003
YOU'RE DEAD!

320
00:21:28,269 --> 00:21:30,936
- [NARAKU LAUGHS]

321
00:21:35,136 --> 00:21:37,069
- AH!

322
00:21:37,103 --> 00:21:39,469
UNH!

323
00:21:44,069 --> 00:21:44,869
- HMM?

324
00:21:44,903 --> 00:21:48,769
PERHAPS I OVERESTIMATED
SESSHOMARU.

325
00:21:49,969 --> 00:21:51,603
- OUT OF MY WAY!

326
00:21:52,303 --> 00:21:54,603
WINDSCAR!

327
00:21:58,303 --> 00:22:00,103
STEP ASIDE!

328
00:22:00,136 --> 00:22:02,569
RRAAH!

329
00:22:03,669 --> 00:22:05,836
- SESSHOMARU MAY BE DOOMED,

330
00:22:05,869 --> 00:22:06,669
BUT WITH THAT SWORD,

331
00:22:06,703 --> 00:22:09,703
INUYASHA COULD
PROBABLY DEFEAT NARAKU.

332
00:22:09,736 --> 00:22:12,603
THEN I WOULD BE FREE.

333
00:22:26,545 --> 00:22:29,278
