THAT INUYASHA WOULD COME HERE.

339
00:24:03,227 --> 00:24:05,793
- I FOUND YOU, NARAKU.
AND THIS TIME, I'LL KILL YOU.

340
00:24:05,827 --> 00:24:10,360
- FOOL. I'VE COMPLETELY ABSORBED
SESSHOMARU'S POWER INTO MY BODY.

341
00:24:10,393 --> 00:24:13,427
